HEADWORD: Patness
<hw>Pat"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Fitness or appropriateness;
striking suitableness; convenience.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The description with equal <qex>patness</qex> may suit both.</q>
<rj><qau>Barrow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

